      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manorhaven%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Manorhaven Beach Park opened around 1936, revitalizing the village’s waterfront along Manhasset Bay.",
